16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_ISDN_20_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_ISDN_20_C

19#define RRTYPE_ISDN_ATTRIBUTES (0)

21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_isdn(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(rdclass);
29 UNUSED(origin);
30 UNUSED(options);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 /* ISDN-address */
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_qstring,
35 false));
36 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
37
38 /* sa: optional */
39 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_qstring,
40 true));
41 if (token.type != isc_tokentype_string &&
42 token.type != isc_tokentype_qstring) {
43 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
44 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
45 }
46 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
47 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51totext_isdn(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
52 isc_region_t region;
53
54 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
55 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
56
57 UNUSED(tctx);
58
59 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
60 RETERR(txt_totext(&region, true, target));
61 if (region.length == 0)
62 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
63 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
64 return (txt_totext(&region, true, target));
65}
66
67static inline isc_result_t
68fromwire_isdn(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
69 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
70
71 UNUSED(type);
72 UNUSED(dctx);
73 UNUSED(rdclass);
74 UNUSED(options);
75
76 RETERR(txt_fromwire(source, target));
77 if (buffer_empty(source))
78 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
79 return (txt_fromwire(source, target));
80}
81
82static inline isc_result_t
83towire_isdn(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
84 UNUSED(cctx);
85
86 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
87 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
88
89 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
90}
91
92static inline int
93compare_isdn(ARGS_COMPARE) {
94 isc_region_t r1;
95 isc_region_t r2;
96
97 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
98 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
99 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
100 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
101 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
102
103 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
104 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
105 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
106}
107
108static inline isc_result_t
109fromstruct_isdn(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
110 dns_rdata_isdn_t *isdn = source;
111
112 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
113 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
114 REQUIRE(isdn->common.rdtype == type);
115 REQUIRE(isdn->common.rdclass == rdclass);
116
117 UNUSED(type);
118 UNUSED(rdclass);
119
120 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(isdn->isdn_len, target));
121 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, isdn->isdn, isdn->isdn_len));
122 if (isdn->subaddress == NULL)
123 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
124 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(isdn->subaddress_len, target));
125 return (mem_tobuffer(target, isdn->subaddress, isdn->subaddress_len));
126}
127
128static inline isc_result_t
129tostruct_isdn(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
130 dns_rdata_isdn_t *isdn = target;
131 isc_region_t r;
132
133 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
134 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
135 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
136
137 isdn->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
138 isdn->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
139 ISC_LINK_INIT(&isdn->common, link);
140
141 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
142
143 isdn->isdn_len = uint8_fromregion(&r);
144 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
145 isdn->isdn = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, isdn->isdn_len);
146 if (isdn->isdn == NULL)
147 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
148 isc_region_consume(&r, isdn->isdn_len);
149
150 if (r.length == 0) {
151 isdn->subaddress_len = 0;
152 isdn->subaddress = NULL;
153 } else {
154 isdn->subaddress_len = uint8_fromregion(&r);
155 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
156 isdn->subaddress = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base,
157 isdn->subaddress_len);
158 if (isdn->subaddress == NULL)
159 goto cleanup;
160 }
161
162 isdn->mctx = mctx;
163 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
164
165 cleanup:
166 if (mctx != NULL && isdn->isdn != NULL)
167 isc_mem_free(mctx, isdn->isdn);
168 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
169}
170
171static inline void
172freestruct_isdn(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
173 dns_rdata_isdn_t *isdn = source;
174
175 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
176
177 if (isdn->mctx == NULL)
178 return;
179
180 if (isdn->isdn != NULL)
181 isc_mem_free(isdn->mctx, isdn->isdn);
182 if (isdn->subaddress != NULL)
183 isc_mem_free(isdn->mctx, isdn->subaddress);
184 isdn->mctx = NULL;
185}

187static inline isc_result_t
188additionaldata_isdn(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
189 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
190
191 UNUSED(rdata);
192 UNUSED(add);
193 UNUSED(arg);
194
195 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
196}
197
198static inline isc_result_t
199digest_isdn(ARGS_DIGEST) {
200 isc_region_t r;
201
202 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
203
204 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
205
206 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
207}

209static inline bool
210checkowner_isdn(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
211
212 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
213
214 UNUSED(name);
215 UNUSED(type);
216 UNUSED(rdclass);
217 UNUSED(wildcard);
218
219 return (true);
220}

222static inline bool
223checknames_isdn(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
224
225 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_isdn);
226
227 UNUSED(rdata);
228 UNUSED(owner);
229 UNUSED(bad);
230
231 return (true);
232}

234static inline int
235casecompare_isdn(ARGS_COMPARE) {
236 return (compare_isdn(rdata1, rdata2));
237}
